snippet.title: Weekly Reliv -Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Episodes 3753-3758 | 24th April To 29th April 2023
snippet.description:
Weekly Reliv is a special compilation of the week’s episodes and is created to give the viewer a feel of the show’s story and its high points. The weekly Reliv here is created especially for the viewers who have missed the week’s episodes and would like to catch up on the plot of their favorite shows. Watch the Weekly Reliv of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah of the episodes from 24th April To 29th April 2023.

Show Name: Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast: Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Raj Anadkat, Amit Bhatt
Episode No: 3753-3758 |  24th April To 29th April 2023
Produced By: Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah 
#तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा 
#SAB  

Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - Promoolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son pushes Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalaal.

Click to watch all the Weekly Reliv episodes: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cQAArE7eMbgq1G5iSXJ7tZC

Weekly Reliv -Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Episodes 3753-3758 | 24th April To 29th April 2023

snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 40 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 40 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 2nd May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma

Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 41 Teaser - 2nd May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3760 - 2 May 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3760: Chamatkari Baba
--------------------------------------------------------
Everyone is informed by Nattu Kaka and Bagha that the person who removed the ink from the coupon has asked them not to expose his identity. Bagha tells everyone that the person who is behind removing the ink from the coupon is a 'chamatkari baba'. Bagha gives a hint to the members of Gokuldham society that they can meet the baba anytime. Taarak solves the riddle given by Bagha and points out Iyer. How has Iyer solved the problem? Remain tuned!
 
Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3760, 2 May 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:
Watch the Full Episode of the bengali serial "Nayantara" which airs on Sun Bangla TV.
 
 Watch all Sun Bangla Full episodes FREE on SUN NXT App. Offer Valid only in India and Bangladesh, till 31th March. 
  
 Download here: 
 Android - http://bit.ly/SunNxtAdroid 
 iOS: India - http://bit.ly/sunNXT 
 Watch on the web - https://www.sunnxt.com/
 
 Nayantara: After 10 years of marriage, Adidev (Gourab Mondal) and Averi (Payal De) are about to experience parenthood with the birth of their first child. The doctor warns Avery that she might face life threatening complications if she decides to go ahead with the child birth. Averi does not tell Adidev about this because she wants to give him the happiness of fatherhood and be a mother herself. On the other hand, Avery means the world to Adidev, so he will definitely chose her life over the child. Avery gives birth to Tara (Hiya Mukherjee). Avery dies within a few minutes of Taraâ€™s birth. The doctor informs Adidev that he had warned Avery but she did not listen. Adidev, who was already devastated by his wife's death, comes to know that the Income Tax Department had raided his office. Adidev starts to believe that Tara is the source of the misfortune in his life and hatred grows in his heart for Tara. On the other hand, Adidev's second wife Madhuja (Swarnakamal) loves Tara more than her own daughter Preeti. But Adideb canâ€™t tolerate that either. Tara's only wish, will she ever get his father's affection?

ਜੱਦੋਂ ਢੋਲ🥁 ਦੀ ਆਵੇ ਆਵਾਜ਼... ਤਾ ਕੋਈ ਥਿਰਕਣ ਤੋਂ ਕਿਵੇ ਰੋਕੇ ਆਪੇ ਪਰ💃... ਖਾਨਾ-ਪੀਣਾ ਤੇ ਨਚਨਾ-ਗੌਣਾ, ਤੁਸੀ ਵੀ ਨਾ ਕਰੋ ਕਾਬੂ... ਪੂਰ ਪਰਿਵਾਰ ਦੇ ਨਾਲ ਆਇਓ ਜ਼ਰੂਰ...

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3759 - 1 May 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3759: Jethalal's Letter
--------------------------------------------------------
Rustom Ji distributes the prizes to the other winners after the photo shoot with the brand-new vehicle. To commemorate the occasion, Iyer, Babita, and Jetha together cut the cake. Jetha asks Rustom Ji to extend Popatlal's prize's validity while she hands out the prizes. Babita and the other Gokuldham show Jethalal their affection and appreciation for organizing such an enjoyable lucky draw. Jethalal's letter suddenly reappears and lands in front of Babita. Babita begins reading the letter aloud with enthusiasm. What will happen once Babita has finished reading it? Remain tuned!
 
Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3759, 1 May 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Episode 3759: Jethalal's Letter
--------------------------------------------------------
Rustom Ji distributes the prizes to the other winners after the photo shoot with the brand-new vehicle. To commemorate the occasion, Iyer, Babita, and Jetha together cut the cake. Jetha asks Rustom Ji to extend Popatlal's prize's validity while she hands out the prizes. Babita and the other Gokuldham show Jethalal their affection and appreciation for organizing such an enjoyable lucky draw. Jethalal's letter suddenly reappears and lands in front of Babita. ilamai ilamai kaadhal
penmaname maname thedal
kanmanikalithivarude koode koodal

aluvaa chiriyal konjal
kanmunayal palathum chollal
mey adimudi idayana minnal..minnal

neeyen azhakiya raani
vaavaa sarigama paadi
pokum vazhikalilai ninn pinnil naamille..

prayam palavidha vyadhi
ennum sirakalil aadhi
nenjil thakiladi thullum thaalam neeyalle..

panjarathen thottam

Panjarakachodam

Murivekaruthe

Kanivekidane..

snippet.title: Ajit Pawar To Supriya Sule: "सुप्रिया तू बोलू नको"; अजित पवारांनी सर्वांसमोर खडसावलं | Sharad Pawar
snippet.description:
NCP chief Sharad Pawar announced his retirement from the post of NCP president, but this time the NCP workers became very emotional. He opposed Pawar's decision in the House. However, in such an emotional atmosphere, Ajit Pawar has given a warning to MP Supriya Pawar-Sule in the Hall. "Supriya you don't talk"; Saying this, Ajit Pawar has challenged everyone.

राष्ट्रवादीचे सर्वेसर्वा शरद पवार यांनी राष्ट्रवादीच्या अध्यक्षपदावरून निवृत्त होण्याची घोषणा केली, मात्र यावेळी राष्ट्रवादीचे कार्यकर्ते प्रचंड भावूक झाले. त्यांनी पवारांच्या निर्णयाला विरोध करत सभागृहात केली. मात्र अशा भावूक वातावरणात अजित पवार यांनी खासदार सुप्रिया पवार-सुळे यांना भर सभागृहात तंबी दिली आहे. "सुप्रिया तू बोलू नको"; असं म्हणत अजित पवारांनी सर्वांसमोर खडसावलं आहे.

Cricket is a bat-and-ball game played between two teams of eleven players. A 22-yard (20-meter) pitch has a wicket at each end, two bails balanced on three stumps. The batting side scores runs by striking the ball bowled at the wicket with the bat (and running between the wickets). In contrast, the bowling and fielding side tries to prevent this (by preventing the ball from leaving the field and getting the ball to either wicket) and dismiss each batter (so they are "out"). Means of dismissal include bowling when the ball hits the stumps and dislodges the bails. The innings ended when ten batters were dismissed, and the teams swapped roles. The game is adjudicated by two umpires, aided by a third umpire and match referee in international matches.

Forms of cricket range from Twenty20, with each team batting for a single inning of 20 overs, to Test matches played over five days. Traditionally, cricketers play in an all-white kit, but they wear club or team colors in limited-overs cricket. In addition to the basic kit, some players wear protective gear to prevent injury caused by the ball. A complex, solid spheroid made of compressed leather with a slightly raised sewn seam enclosing a cork core layered tightly wound string.

snippet.title: PAV BHAJI | Mumbai Special Street Food Recipe Cooking In Village | Butter Pav Bhaji Recipe
snippet.description: Today we cook Mumbai Special street food Pav Bhaji recipe, with our beloved grandpa. In this cooking video, you'll get a glimpse of our traditional way of preparing this popular Indian street food with fresh ingredients. From chopping vegetables to slow-cooking the Bhaji, you'll witness every step of the process as we bond and have fun together. So sit back, relax, and get ready to feast your eyes on this culinary adventure in the heart of the village. Don't forget to try this recipe at home, and let us know how it turns out!

*About* 
------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

*About* 
------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

snippet.title: Lovely ने बताया सब! | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 700
snippet.description:
Lovely ने बताया सब! | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 700

Samar rescues Bani, while everybody catches hold of Lovely and compels her to tell the truth. What comes after is a shocking revelation when Lovely reveals that she is connected to Thapki's past. Who is Lovely and how is she connected to Thapki?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3758 - 29 Apr 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3758: Car Ka Golmol
--------------------------------------------------------
Everyone has been waiting for the car delivery, so Babita Ji questions Jethalal about it. Since Jetha is hesitant to respond, everyone begins to question him repeatedly. Tapu Sena tries to stop Iyer as he becomes ecstatic in response to their surprise. People in Gokhuldham hear music band troops playing and a brand-new red automobile pulling up suddenly. Has the car actually shown up yet? Remain tuned!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3758, 29 Apr 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000218407

snippet.title: Ladakh tests World's First Mountain Top Lifi Laser 5G internet | Sonam Wangchuk
snippet.description:
In this video, we explore the groundbreaking technology that is being tested in Ladakh - the world's first mountain-top LiFi laser 5G internet. Despite the harsh winter conditions, this technology has been successfully tested for two consecutive winters, bringing high-speed internet connectivity to the Secmol school. Join us as we delve into the details of this innovative technology and how it is transforming the way we connect with the world, even in the most challenging terrain

►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

About CID: 
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

snippet.description:
Abhijit Gangopadhyay : নিয়োগ দুর্নীতি মামলার ভবিষ্যৎ নিয়ে আশঙ্কা প্রকাশ। সুপ্রিম কোর্টের নির্দেশে মান্যতা দিয়েও প্রতিবাদী থাকার আশ্বাস বিচারপতি অভিজিৎ গঙ্গোপাধ্যায়ের। বাড়ির সামনে দাঁড়িয়ে শোনা গেল অভিমানী স্বর। 

#abhijitgangopadhyay #supremecourt #reccruitmentscam #news18bangla #banglanews
n180c_kolkata

snippet.title: बाहर आया सच! | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 699
snippet.description:
बाहर आया सच! | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 699

Thapki finally reveals it all! Aryan gets to know how Lovely had held her and Bani as hostages and ruthlessly tortured them. What follows next is a shocking discovery as the Pandey family meets the girl behind the veil! Can Aryan and Thapki rescue Bani? Will Lovely get to know about their plan? Tune in to find out!

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

snippet.title: 200 Years Old Silver Making Technique - असली चांदी का आईना | MR. INDIAN HACKER
snippet.description:
How To Make Silver Mirror At Home Using Only Chemicals.

Ab Description Dekh Hi Liya Hai To Follow Bhi Kar Lo -

Instagram - https://instagram.com/Dilraj_Singh_Rawat

Twitter - https://twitter.com/MR_INDIANHACKER

#mrindianhacker 


Explanation of Experiment:

The mirror forms when a thin film of metallic silver deposits on the inner surface of the flask. When an aldehyde is combined with an ammonia complex of silver in a basic aqueous solution, the aldehyde slowly reduces the complex to silver metal.

snippet.title: Lakshana | ಲಕ್ಷಣ | Episode 447 | Highlights
snippet.description:
Catch All the Action on Jio Cinema: https://www.jiocinema.com/
Android - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jio.media.ondemand
iOS - https://apps.apple.com/in/app/jiocinema/id1067316596

ಪೊಲೀಸ್ ಆಯುಕ್ತರಿಂದ ಶ್ವೇತಾಳ ಫೋನ್ ಕರೆ ವಿವರಗಳನ್ನು ಸಿಎಸ್ ಪಡೆಯುತ್ತಾನೆ. ಮಹಿಳೆಯೊಬ್ಬಳ ಸಂಖ್ಯೆಗೆ ಶ್ವೇತಾ ಅನೇಕ ಬಾರಿ ಕರೆ ಮಾಡಿರುವುದನ್ನು ಅವನು ಗಮನಿಸಿಸುತ್ತಾನೆ. ಈ ಮಹಿಳೆ ಡೆವಿಲ್ ಎಂದು ಅವನು ಅನುಮಾನಿಸುತ್ತಾನೆ.

CS gets the call details of Shwetha's phone from the police commissioner. He notices that Shwetha had called to one lady's number many times. He suspects that this lady is the Devil.

#ColorsKannada #Lakshana

The talented dusky beauty Nakshatra dreams of becoming a TV Anchor but faces pushback. When she finally does manage to land a job, she is only the voice, while Shwetha, is the face of the show. Trouble begins when Bhupathi falls in love with her voice, while believing that it's Shwetha's. Follow Nakshatra's journey as she takes on the world & it's prejudice, in Lakshana. 

Watch more videos - https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLJRM1-EkjJa6Rf3exCqkKc0ECFNMO2W6j

Follow us on: 
https://www.facebook.com/colorskannada
https://www.instagram.com/colorskannadaofficial/
